Release 3.2
-----------

Features added
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* The call to ``get`` can now take an optional default value. More details can
  be found in the docstring.


Release 3.1
-----------

Features added
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* It is now possible to extend the search path by prefixing the
  ``<APP_NAME>_PATH`` variable value with a ``+``

* Changelog added


